{"type":null,"faqId":48086,"title":"设置帐户","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">添加帐户</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"账户\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178140\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“帐户”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>点击“添加帐户”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span>选择一个帐户类型。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">5.  </span><span>按照屏幕提示输入帐户相关信息。</span><a name=\"_task_remove_account-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 删除帐户</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"删除帐户\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178141\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.在“全部设置”页签下，点击“帐户”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.在“帐户”界面，选择一个帐户类型。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.选择要删除的帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5.按照界面的提示，删除帐户。</span><a name=\"_task_start_sync-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">开启电子邮件同步功能</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"同步\"XE \"帐户同步\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178142\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.在“全部设置”页签下，点击“帐户”。 </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178143\" style=\"width:0.25694445in;height:0.18333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”,勾选“自动同步数据”，按照屏幕提示点击“确定”，开启同步数据开关。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.在“帐户”界面，选择一个帐户类型。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5.选择要开启同步的帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>6.点击“同步电子邮件”开关，开启帐户同步功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3672","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598115000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":106,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}